### Health
GET http://localhost:8002/health

### English question
POST http://localhost:8002/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "When should I plant maize in Lagos this season?",
  "state": "Lagos",
  "crop": "Maize"
}

### Pidgin question (auto-detected)
POST http://localhost:8002/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Abeg, my tomato dey die small small for Kaduna. Wetin I go do?"
}

### USSD first dial
POST http://localhost:8002/v1/ussd
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "s1",
  "serviceCode": "*789#",
  "phoneNumber": "+2348012345678",
  "text": ""
}

### USSD: pick Maize -> Fertiliser
POST http://localhost:8002/v1/ussd
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "s1",
  "serviceCode": "*789#",
  "phoneNumber": "+2348012345678",
  "text": "1*2"
}

### Image diagnosis (replace image_b64 with a real base64 leaf photo)
POST http://localhost:8002/v1/diagnose
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is wrong with my maize leaf?",
  "image_b64": "REPLACE_WITH_BASE64",
  "image_media_type": "image/jpeg",
  "state": "Kaduna",
  "crop": "Maize"
}
